BASH Shortcuts
pwd	print working directory	shows where you are
ls	list directory	shows what’s in the directory
ls *fastq	print anything that has the fastq ending	
ls /bin	search within the bin folder w/o actually being in that folder	
*	wildcard	sub anything into the spot
wc	word count	
wc -l	count the number of lines	wc -l filename.fastq
cd ../	back up one directory	
cd ../../	back up two directories	
mkdir	create a directory	
cp	copy a file	cp SRR098026.fastq SRR098026-backup.fastq
